r1: Spaghetti Bolognese: Ground beef, onion, garlic, tomato sauce, Italian seasoning, spaghetti: Brown beef with onion and garlic. Add tomato sauce and seasoning. Simmer. Serve over cooked spaghetti.
r2: Chicken Alfredo Pasta: Chicken breast, fettuccine, Alfredo sauce, Parmesan cheese, garlic: Cook chicken, slice. Cook pasta. Mix Alfredo sauce with garlic. Toss pasta, chicken, and sauce. Top with Parmesan.
r3: Vegetarian Stir-Fry: Tofu, mixed vegetables, soy sauce, ginger, garlic, rice: Stir-fry tofu and veggies. Add soy sauce, ginger, and garlic.
r4: Grilled Salmon: Salmon fillets, lemon, olive oil, dill, salt, pepper: Marinate salmon in olive oil, lemon juice, and spices. Grill until cooked. Garnish with fresh dill.
r5: Margherita Pizza: Pizza dough, tomato sauce, fresh mozzarella, tomatoes, basil, olive oil: Roll out pizza dough. Spread sauce, add mozzarella, tomatoes, and basil. Drizzle with olive oil. Bake until crust is golden.
r6: Caesar Salad: Romaine lettuce, croutons, Parmesan cheese, Caesar dressing, chicken breast: Toss lettuce, croutons, and Parmesan. Add grilled chicken. Drizzle with Caesar dressing.
r7: Beef Tacos: Ground beef, taco seasoning, tortillas, lettuce, tomato, cheese, salsa: Cook beef with taco seasoning. Fill tortillas with beef, lettuce, tomato, cheese. Top with salsa.
r8: Chicken Noodle Soup: Chicken broth, chicken breast, carrots, celery, onion, noodles: Boil chicken with veggies. Add noodles. Simmer until noodles are cooked. Season to taste.
r9: Caprese Salad: Tomatoes, mozzarella, fresh basil, balsamic glaze, olive oil, salt: Arrange tomato and mozzarella slices. Add basil leaves. Drizzle with olive oil and balsamic glaze. Sprinkle with salt.
r10: Shrimp Scampi: Shrimp, garlic, butter, white wine, lemon, parsley, linguine: Sauté shrimp and garlic in butter. Add white wine, lemon, and parsley. Serve over cooked linguine.
r11: Spinach and Feta Stuffed Chicken: Chicken breast, spinach, feta cheese, garlic, olive oil, salt, pepper: Mix spinach, feta, and garlic. Cut a pocket in chicken. Stuff with mixture. Bake until chicken is cooked.
r12: Quinoa Salad: Quinoa, cucumber, cherry tomatoes, feta, olives, olive oil, lemon: Cook quinoa. Mix with veggies, feta, and olives. Drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice.
r13: BBQ Pulled Pork Sandwiches: Pork shoulder, BBQ sauce, buns, coleslaw: Slow-cook pork with BBQ sauce. Shred. Serve on buns with coleslaw.
r14: Teriyaki Chicken Bowl: Chicken thighs, teriyaki sauce, broccoli, carrots, rice: Cook chicken with teriyaki sauce. Steam veggies. Serve over rice.
r15: Eggplant Parmesan: Eggplant, breadcrumbs, marinara sauce, mozzarella, Parmesan, basil: Bread and bake eggplant. Layer with sauce and cheese. Bake until bubbly. Top with fresh basil.
r16: Greek Salad: Cucumbers, tomatoes, olives, red onion, feta, olive oil, oregano: Mix veggies, olives, and feta. Drizzle with olive oil. Sprinkle with oregano.
r17: Chicken Fajitas: Chicken strips, bell peppers, onions, fajita seasoning, tortillas: Sauté chicken with veggies and seasoning. Serve in tortillas.
r18: Mushroom Risotto: Arborio rice, mushrooms, chicken broth, onion, Parmesan, white wine: Sauté mushrooms and onion. Add rice, wine, and broth. Stir until creamy. Top with Parmesan.
r19: Tuna Salad Wrap: Canned tuna, mayonnaise, celery, lettuce, whole wheat wraps: Mix tuna, mayo, and celery. Spread on wraps with lettuce. Roll up and enjoy.
r20: Lentil Soup: Lentils, carrots, celery, onion, garlic, vegetable broth: Cook lentils with veggies and broth. Simmer until vegetables are tender.
r21: Margarita Chicken: Chicken thighs, lime, tequila, triple sec, cilantro, salt: Marinate chicken in lime, tequila, and triple sec. Grill. Garnish with cilantro and salt.
r22: Sweet Potato and Black Bean Burritos: Sweet potatoes, black beans, onions, salsa, tortillas: Roast sweet potatoes. Mix with beans and onions. Fill tortillas and top with salsa.
r23: Pesto Pasta with Cherry Tomatoes: Pasta, pesto sauce, cherry tomatoes, Parmesan cheese: Cook pasta. Toss with pesto, cherry tomatoes, and Parmesan.
r24: Beef and Broccoli Stir-Fry: Beef strips, broccoli, soy sauce, ginger, garlic, rice: Stir-fry beef and broccoli in soy sauce, ginger, and garlic. Serve over rice.
r25: Roasted Vegetable Pizza: Pizza dough, tomato sauce, bell peppers, zucchini, red onion, mozzarella: Top pizza dough with sauce, veggies, and cheese. Bake until crust is golden.
r26: Chicken Caesar Wraps: Chicken strips, romaine lettuce, Caesar dressing, Parmesan cheese, flour tortillas: Wrap chicken, lettuce, dressing, and Parmesan in tortillas.
r27: Mango Salsa Chicken: Chicken breasts, mango, red onion, cilantro, lime, salt: Grill chicken. Top with mango salsa made with diced mango, onion, cilantro, lime, and salt.
r28: Avocado and Black Bean Salad: Avocado, black beans, corn, red onion, lime, cilantro: Mix diced avocado, black beans, corn, and onion. Squeeze lime, add cilantro. Toss and serve.
r29: Thai Peanut Noodles: Rice noodles, chicken, bell peppers, peanuts, cilantro, peanut sauce: Cook noodles. Sauté chicken and peppers. Toss with noodles, peanuts, cilantro, and peanut sauce.
r30: Lemon Garlic Shrimp Pasta: Shrimp, linguine, garlic, lemon, butter, parsley: Sauté shrimp and garlic in butter. Toss with cooked linguine.
